パッケージの使用
org.interledger.codecs.oer

  • org.interledger.codecs.oerを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger.codecs.oer  
  • org.interledger.codecs.oerにより使用されるorg.interledger.codecs.oerのクラス 
    クラスと説明
    OerGeneralizedTimeCodec.OerGeneralizedTime
    A typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type, in this case ZonedDateTime.
    OerIA5StringCodec.OerIA5String
    A typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type (in this case, String).
    OerLengthPrefixCodec.OerLengthPrefix
    An typing mechanism for registering codecs for length prefixes (as opposed to normal integer types).
    OerOctetStringCodec.OerOctetString
    A typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type (in this case, byte[]).
    OerSequenceOfAddressCodec.OerSequenceOfAddress
    An typing mechanism for registering codecs.
    OerUint256Codec.OerUint256
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
    OerUint32Codec.OerUint32
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
    OerUint64Codec.OerUint64
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
    OerUint8Codec.OerUint8
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
